### 1. Call Tasks API without token (should fail with 401)
GET http://localhost:5138/api/tasks
Accept: application/json


### 2. Login via Identity to get JWT
POST http://localhost:5138/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ahmed@example.com",
  "password": "@aA12345678"
}

> {% client.global.set("token", response.body.token); %}

### 3. Call Tasks API with JWT
GET http://localhost:5138/api/tasks
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
